1
00:00:00,885 --> 00:00:03,240
One morning, Humf looked out of the window.
一个早晨  Humf看向窗外

2
00:00:03,250 --> 00:00:05,120
Everything had white on it.
一切都被白雪淹没了

3
00:00:06,580 --> 00:00:10,460
There were more little bit of white falling from the sky, too.
还有一些白雪从天空缓缓落下

4
00:00:10,600 --> 00:00:13,400
Snow! It's snowing!
雪哎   下雪了

5
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:18,245
Let's all go to the park. Come on, Humf. 
我们都去公园吧  来吧  Humf

6
00:00:18,251 --> 00:00:20,897
You want to go play in the snow, don't you?
你不是就喜欢在雪里玩儿吗

7
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:24,560
Humf's mom and dad were very excited.
Humf的爸爸妈妈都很兴奋

8
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:26,400
Better dress warmly, Humf.
我们要穿暖和点哦  Humf

9
00:00:26,420 --> 00:00:28,700
It's going to be cold in the snow.
雪里很冷的

10
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:33,440
What about breakfast?
早饭怎么办

11
00:00:33,480 --> 00:00:35,600
We can have some breakfast when we come back.
我们回来的时候可以吃点早饭

12
00:00:37,340 --> 00:00:42,120
Humf couldn't see his fingers now, just big red mittens!
Humf现在看不到他的手指了 只有红色的手套了

13
00:00:42,660 --> 00:00:44,120
Is everybody ready?
每个人都准备好了吗

14
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,260
Yes.
是的

